data.description: Have you outgrown your current home?  Needing more space?  Look no further! This 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath, open concept home might be just what you are looking for.  The main floor features a large kitchen open to the dining and living rooms, main floor laundry/mudroom off the attached 2 car garage, master bedroom with large updated master bath, 2 additional bedrooms, 1 full bath and the half bath.  Down on the lower level you will find the recently updated large family room, 2 brand new bedrooms, and the 3rd updated full bath.  Not to mention the new furnace and ac units. Both installed March 2023. All situated on 3.17 acres on the edge of town.  Call your favorite realtor today!
